name: JAILAXMI EDUCATION SOCIETY

address: Gokul Nagar, Next to Hotel United 21,

briefDescription: "JaiLaxmi Education Society" (JLES) is a Non-profit Organisation, founded in 2012.JLES has its core focus towards Skills Development of underprivileged youth with a successful track record of skilling 1300 of which 80% have been connected to Livelihood opportunities so far.JLES is the renowned Employment oriented Professional Skill Training & Educational Institute in India producing 'Qualified & Skilled Professionals, by training more than 2500 candidates across Maharashtra, Gujarat, Rajasthan, Madhya Pradesh and Goa with our extensive reach and employed globally JLES offers a proven, updated and innovative content and skill-based training to achieve CSR goals and make a valuable contribution towards helping the 350 million + youth.
